OL,3,CGovernment U-turns on mandatory
OL,4,Cdigital ID cards
OL,6,FThe government is backing down on its
OL,7,Fplan for mandatory digital ID cards
OL,8,Ffor anyone wanting to get a job in the
OL,9,FUK.
OL,11,FThis tells us two things; one about
OL,12,Fthe hole the government is in, and
OL,13,Fanother about how it means to climb
OL,14,Fout.
OL,16,FThe plan, announced by the prime
OL,17,Fminister in September, was intended to
OL,18,Fhelp crack down on the apparent ease
OL,19,Fwith which migrants can work illegally
OL,20,Fin the UK.
