OL,6,FYouGov found the number of people
OL,7,Fopposed to ID cards rocketed from 25%
OL,8,Fbefore his announcement to 47% after
OL,9,Fit.
OL,11,FThis is not the effect you want your
OL,12,Fcheerleader-in-chief to have on your
OL,13,Fpolicies.
OL,15,FBut Tuesday's U-turn also tells us
OL,16,Fthat Keir Starmer sees a way out of
OL,17,Fthis hole.
